<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rental Agreement</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 1in;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 6.5in;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24pt;
            margin-bottom: 0.5in;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 0.2in;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .underline {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 0.75in;
            text-align: left;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .signature-party {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 2.5in;
            margin: 0.2in auto 0.05in auto;
        }
        .date-place {
            margin-top: 0.5in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 1in;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Rental Agreement</h1>

        <div class="section">
            This Rental Agreement is made and entered into on this <span class="bold underline">{{ agreement_start_date | default(current_date) }}</span>,
            between:
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">LANDLORD:</span></p>
            <p><span class="bold underline">{{ landlord_name | default("[Landlord's Full Name]") }}</span>, son/daughter/wife of <span class="bold underline">{{ landlord_father_name | default("[Landlord's Father/Husband's Name]") }}</span>,
            residing at <span class="bold underline">{{ landlord_address | default("[Landlord's Full Address]") }}</span>.</p>
            <p>(hereinafter referred to as the "Landlord", which expression shall unless repugnant to the context or meaning thereof, include his/her heirs, executors, administrators and assigns)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">AND</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">TENANT:</span></p>
            <p><span class="bold underline">{{ tenant_name | default("[Tenant's Full Name]") }}</span>, son/daughter/wife of <span class="bold underline">{{ tenant_father_name | default("[Tenant's Father/Husband's Name]") }}</span>,
            residing at <span class="bold underline">{{ tenant_address | default("[Tenant's Full Address]") }}</span>.</p>
            <p>(hereinafter referred to as the "Tenant", which expression shall unless repugnant to the context or meaning thereof, include his/her heirs, executors, administrators and assigns)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">WHEREAS</span> the Landlord is the absolute owner of the property situated at:</p>
            <p class="bold underline">{{ property_address | default("[Full Address of the Property being Rented]") }}</p>
            <p>(hereinafter referred to as the "Said Property").</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>AND WHEREAS the Tenant has approached the Landlord to take the Said Property on rent for residential/commercial purposes for a period of <span class="bold underline">{{ lease_duration | default("[Lease Duration, e.g., '11 months', '2 years']") }}</span>, commencing from <span class="bold underline">{{ agreement_start_date | default(current_date) }}</span> and ending on <span class="bold underline">{{ agreement_end_date | default("[Agreement End Date]") }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">NOW THIS AGREEMENT WITNESSETH AS FOLLOWS:</span></p>
            <ol>
                <li>That the monthly rent for the Said Property shall be <span class="bold underline">Rs. {{ rent_amount | default("[Rent Amount in Figures]") }} /- (Rupees {{ rent_amount_words | default("[Rent Amount in Words]") }} Only)</span>, payable on or before the <span class="bold underline">{{ rent_due_date | default("5th") }}</span> day of each calendar month.</li>
                <li>That the Tenant shall pay a Security Deposit of <span class="bold underline">Rs. {{ security_deposit | default("[Security Deposit Amount in Figures]") }} /- (Rupees {{ security_deposit_words | default("[Security Deposit Amount in Words]") }} Only)</span> to the Landlord, which shall be refundable at the time of vacating the Said Property, subject to deductions for any damages or unpaid dues.</li>
                <li>That the Tenant shall use the Said Property for <span class="bold underline">{{ property_usage | default("residential") }}</span> purposes only.</li>
                <li>That the Tenant shall be responsible for all utility bills including electricity, water, and maintenance charges.</li>
                <li>That the Tenant shall maintain the Said Property in good and tenantable condition.</li>
                <li><span class="bold">Other Terms and Conditions:</span> {{ terms_and_conditions | default("[Any other specific terms and conditions agreed upon by both parties, e.g., 'No pets allowed', 'Subletting not permitted', 'Notice period for vacating the property']") }}</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties have executed this Agreement on the date first above written.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="signature-party">
                <p>WITNESSES:</p>
                <p>1. _________________________</p>
                <p>2. _________________________</p>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-party">
                <p>LANDLORD</p>
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <p class="bold">{{ landlord_name | default("[Landlord's Full Name]") }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-party">
                <p>TENANT</p>
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <p class="bold">{{ tenant_name | default("[Tenant's Full Name]") }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="date-place">
            <p>Date: {{ current_date }}</p>
            <p>Place: {{ place | default("[Place]") }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
